OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1781387267
OL,3,CPolice officer, 19, dies after
OL,4,Ccollision while responding to another
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FA 19-year-old police officer has died
OL,8,Fin hospital after she was hit by a car
OL,9,Fwhile responding to another collision,
OL,10,Fher chief constable has said.
OL,12,FPc Jess Turnbull, who had only joined
OL,13,FNorthumbria Police in September, was
OL,14,Fcalled to a collision on the A189 near
OL,15,FCramlington, Northumberland, at around
OL,16,F11.10pm on Monday.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/6
