PN,42402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1781387267
OL,3,CPolice officer, 19, dies after
OL,4,Ccollision while responding to another
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FNorthumbria Police said that while she
OL,8,Fwas out of her marked police vehicle
OL,9,Fat the scene, Pc Turnbull was struck
OL,10,Fby a black Mercedes CLC that was
OL,11,Funconnected to the original incident.
OL,13,FChief Constable Vanessa Jardine said
OL,14,FPc Turnbull died in hospital on
OL,15,FWednesday, surrounded by her loved
OL,16,Fones.
OL,18,FShe worked for the response policing
OL,19,Fteam in Northumberland.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1781387267
OL,3,CPolice officer, 19, dies after
OL,4,Ccollision while responding to another
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FMs Jardine paid tribute to the young
OL,8,Fofficer at the force's headquarters in
OL,9,FNorth Tyneside, where the Union flag
OL,10,Fwas at half mast.
OL,12,FShe said: "This is an extremely tragic
OL,13,Fincident where Jess lost her life in
OL,14,Fthe line of duty while serving and
OL,15,Fprotecting our communities.
OL,17,F"Our thoughts very much continue to be
OL,18,Fwith her family, friends and all those
OL,19,Fwho have been impacted by this
OL,20,Fdevastating loss.
OL,26,@tD@KOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
