OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1781387267
OL,3,CPolice officer, 19, dies after
OL,4,Ccollision while responding to another
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,F"Jess was relatively new in service
OL,8,Fwith so much still to look forward to
OL,9,Fin her career and life.
OL,11,F"She was a dedicated and committed
OL,12,Fofficer who always sought to do her
OL,13,Fbest to keep her communities safe."
OL,15,FNorthumbria Police said a 73-year-old
OL,16,Fman was arrested at the scene on
OL,17,Fsuspicion of causing serious injury by
OL,18,Fdangerous driving.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/6
