PN,42405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1781387267
OL,3,CPolice officer, 19, dies after
OL,4,Ccollision while responding to another
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FHe was taken to hospital but has been
OL,8,Freleased. He was re-arrested on
OL,9,Fsuspicion of causing death by
OL,10,Fdangerous driving and has been bailed.
OL,12,FPolice have appealed for witnesses or
OL,13,Fpeople with dashcam footage to come
OL,14,Fforward.People have been urged not to
OL,15,Fleave floral tributes to the officer
OL,16,Fat the scene of the crash for safety
OL,17,Freasons.
OL,19,FThe officer's family has asked for
OL,20,Fprivacy.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
