FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1781387267
OL,3,CPolice officer, 19, dies after
OL,4,Ccollision while responding to another
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FPc Turnbull was responding to a
OL,8,Fcollision involving two cars, with the
OL,9,Foccupants of one of the vehicles
OL,10,Ffleeing the scene.
OL,12,FIt was understood Pc Turnbull was the
OL,13,Ffirst Northumbria Police officer to be
OL,14,Fkilled on duty since 2006 when Pc
OL,15,FJoseph Carroll was fatally injured in
OL,16,Fa collision caused by a prisoner he
OL,17,Fwas transporting pulling the handbrake
OL,18,Fon his car.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/6
